{"id":"pattern-mini-001","type":"pattern","fact":"External services are tested by record-and-replay: fakes in tests/helpers replay recorded JSON fixtures in tests/fixtures. New branches are covered by adding a fixture, not by editing mock logic.","recommendation":"To cover a new edge (timeout, 401/404, malformed JSON), capture the real interaction and drop a fixture; keep recorded fixtures separate from how the fake selects one.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"human","reference":"CLAUDE.md testing rules","date":"2026-06-23"}],"tags":["testing","fixtures","fakes"],"affectedFiles":["tests/helpers/mock-context.js","tests/fixtures"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
